            "title": "Heuristische Entscheidungen in der Gruppen bei der Personalauswahl",
            "abstract": "Heuristics are usually discussed as an individual phenomenon, but this raises the question of whether heuristics may also be applied at a collective level. The paper examines this heuristic decision making at a group level. The path of limited rational decision research to heuristic decision phenomena of the organization describes the field of decision research. Information processing, Hidden Profiles and cognitive mapping of groups are crucial factors in the heuristic decisions of groups. These elements will be integrated and investigated. Moreover, this paper will expand the basic rules o...",
